dc:description: Base ring complete; colorless glass with faint greenish tinge; no weathering; material excellent; very few bubbles and impurities.  Bottom slopes downward toward base.  Concave base with tubular base ring.  Raised coil, fused in, in center of under side of base, and a thinner coil trailed horizontally round vase outside base ring.
